msgstr "一次性应用密码"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:737
msgid ""
"Paste it only into the AI client dedicated secret field. Adapter does not "
"grant provider credentials, prompt management, workflow runtime, or Cloud "
"connector authority."
msgstr ""
"只将它粘贴到 AI 客户端的专用密钥字段。Adapter 不授予提供商凭据、提示词管理、"
"工作流运行时或 Cloud 连接器权限。"

