msgid "No recognized Adapter scopes were requested."
msgstr "未请求可识别的 Adapter 权限范围。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:471
msgid ""
"Execute approved Adapter write routes only after Core approval and commit "
"preflight."
msgstr "仅在 Core 批准并完成提交预检后，执行已批准的 Adapter 写入路由。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:470
msgid "Check Adapter, Core proposal, and execution status."
msgstr "检查 Adapter、Core 提案和执行状态。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:469
msgid "Create Core-governed proposals for reviewed writes."
msgstr "为已审核的写入创建由 Core 治理的提案。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:468
msgid "Read approved Adapter and WordPress Abilities API routes."
msgstr "读取已批准的 Adapter 和 WordPress Abilities API 路由。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:454
msgid "Npcink client rejected"
msgstr "Npcink 客户端已拒绝"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:450
msgid "Npcink client approved"
msgstr "Npcink 客户端已批准"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:428
msgid ""
"Optional administrator-only label for later management. It is not used for "
"authentication or authorization. Do not enter passwords, tokens, private "
"keys, or local file paths."
msgstr ""
"可选，仅供管理员后续管理识别。它不参与认证或授权。不要填写密码、令牌、私钥或"
"本地文件路径。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:427
msgid "Example: Muze MacBook or office OpenClaw"
msgstr "例如：Muze MacBook 或办公室 OpenClaw"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:418
msgid "Client key record ID"
msgstr "客户端密钥记录 ID"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:417
msgid "Connection record ID"
msgstr "连接记录 ID"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:415
msgid "Scope IDs"
msgstr "权限范围 ID"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:414
msgid "Public key fingerprint"
msgstr "公钥指纹"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:411
msgid ""
"Do not paste these values into chat, tool commands, proposal payloads, or "
"setup text unless a support workflow explicitly asks for diagnostic "
"identifiers."
msgstr ""
"除非支持流程明确要求诊断标识符，否则不要把这些值粘贴到聊天、工具命令、提案负"
"载或配置文本中。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:409
msgid "IDs and fingerprints for support; these are not client setup secrets."
msgstr "用于支持排查的 ID 和指纹；这些不是客户端配置密钥。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:408
msgid "Diagnostic details"
msgstr "诊断详情"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:404
msgid ""
"This approval does not grant direct WordPress write, approval, publish, "
"provider credential, prompt, model routing, or production workload execution "
"authority. Writes must still go through Core proposal, approval, and commit-"
"preflight; Adapter remains the client channel."
msgstr ""
"此批准不会授予直接 WordPress 写入、审批、发布、提供商凭据、提示词、模型路由或"
"生产工作负载执行权限。写入仍必须经过 Core 提案、审批和提交预检；Adapter 仍然"
"只是客户端通道。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:398
msgid "Requested access"
msgstr "请求的访问权限"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:398
msgid "Approved access"
msgstr "已批准的访问权限"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:393
msgid "Expires"
msgstr "过期时间"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:390
msgid "Approved"
msgstr "批准时间"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:388
msgid "Started"
msgstr "发起时间"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:387
msgid "Used pairing code"
msgstr "已使用的配对代码"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:386
msgid "Local verifier"
msgstr "本地验证程序"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:385
msgid "Device reported by client"
msgstr "客户端报告的设备"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:382
#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:426
msgid "Device note"
msgstr "设备备注"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:370
msgid "Manage paired clients"
msgstr "管理已配对客户端"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:370
msgid ""
"If you did not start this pairing, revoke this client from the Adapter page "
"immediately."
msgstr "如果您没有发起此次配对，请立即在适配器页面撤销此客户端。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:368
msgid ""
"Return to the terminal or local AI client that started pairing. Wait for it "
"to report ready; this browser page can be closed. Adapter stores only the "
"public key; the private key was never sent to WordPress."
msgstr ""
"请返回发起配对的终端或本地 AI 客户端。等待它显示 ready；此浏览器页面可以关"
"闭。适配器只保存公钥；私钥从未发送到 WordPress。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:320
msgid ""
"I understand this fallback creates a WordPress Application Password and the "
"signed key-pair connection is preferred."
msgstr ""
"我理解此备用方式会创建 WordPress 应用密码，且优先推荐使用签名密钥连接。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:298
msgid "Fallback: WordPress Application Password connection"
msgstr "备用：WordPress 应用密码连接"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:291
msgid ""
"Revoke a device when it is no longer used or was approved by mistake. "
"Revoked devices must pair again before they can connect."
msgstr "设备不再使用或误授权时可撤销。撤销后的设备必须重新配对才能连接。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:282
msgid ""
"Run this command on the computer or terminal where OpenClaw is running. "
"Adapter stores only the approved public key."
msgstr ""
"请在运行 OpenClaw 的电脑或终端中运行该命令。Adapter 只保存已批准的公钥。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:280
msgid "Manage devices"
msgstr "管理设备"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:274
msgid ""
"Recommended path: pair a local signed key so the client never receives a "
"WordPress Application Password."
msgstr "推荐路径：配对本地签名密钥，避免客户端接收 WordPress 应用密码。"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:272
msgid "Recommended"
msgstr "推荐"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:271
msgid "Secure key pairing"
msgstr "安全密钥配对"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:253
#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:286
msgid "Active devices"
msgstr "有效设备"

#: includes/Admin/Connection_Page.php:249
