#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5870
msgid ""
"Core authorization context was issued for a different signed local client."
msgstr "Core 授权上下文是为另一个已签名本地客户端签发的。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5856
msgid ""
"Core authorization context signed client fingerprint aliases do not match."
msgstr "Core 授权上下文中的已签名客户端指纹别名不匹配。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5848
msgid ""
"Core authorization context includes an invalid signed client fingerprint."
msgstr "Core 授权上下文包含无效的已签名客户端指纹。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5819
msgid "Core authorization context is expired or missing a valid expiry."
msgstr "Core 授权上下文已过期或缺少有效过期时间。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5715
msgid ""
"Core execution handoff correlation id does not match the commit preflight "
"correlation id."
msgstr "核心执行交接的 correlation id 与提交预检 correlation id 不匹配。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5699
msgid ""
"Core execution handoff ability id does not match the approved proposal or "
"write actions."
msgstr "核心执行交接的能力 ID 与已批准提案或写入动作不匹配。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5684
msgid ""
"Core execution handoff proposal id does not match the Adapter execution "
"request."
msgstr "核心执行交接的提案 ID 与适配器执行请求不匹配。"

#: includes/Rest/Controller.php:5671
msgid ""
"Core execution handoff must keep commit_execution=false before Adapter "
